Nigerian chef and Guinness World Record holder for marathon cooking, Hilda Baci has announced the arrival of her award plaque. Baci via a post on her Instagram page shared the excitingnews. She was certified as the new record holder for the longest cooking by an individual with 93 hours and 11 minutes. In the video, she received the award plaque packaged in a box and delivered by a dispatch rider. She wrote, “Our plaque is here #guinnessworldrecords.”